<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1935-10-12T19:25:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1935-10-12T19:25:00-05:00" n="558" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d558">
                                <note rend="inline" type="source">765.84/1776: Telegram</note>
                                <head>
                                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Ethiopia</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Engert</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                            State</gloss>
                                    </hi>
                                </head>
                                <opener>
                                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                                        <placeName>
                                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Addis Ababa</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-10-13T03:00:00+02:35">October 13, 1935—3 a.m.</date>
                                        <lb/> [Received 9:40 a.m.]</dateline>
                                </opener>
                                <p>127. My 126, October 12, 5 p.m. Another special train was
                                    provided for the Italian Minister at 10 o’clock this morning but
                                    again he refused to go.</p>
                                <p>I am reliably informed that Vinci had a nervous breakdown and
                                    threatened to commit suicide. He is reported to have said that
                                    he felt largely responsible for the apparent failure of Italy’s
                                    policy in Ethiopia.</p>
                                <closer>
                                    <signed>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Engert</hi>
                                    </signed>
                                </closer>
                            </div>
                            </body></text></TEI>